<h5 id="subject_1129219">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=127395.msg1129219#msg1129219" rel="nofollow">黑暗纪元1简介</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1129219'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1129219'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #1 于:</strong> 2021-08-13, 周五 01:49:04 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1129219_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
